                            </div>
                            <div class="col-span-2 row-span-1 rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative group">
                                <img class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" data-alt="A sleek, professional kitchen area within a rental unit featuring stainless steel appliances and white cabinetry. The lighting is crisp and modern, highlighting a clean and efficient workspace. The overall mood is one of controlled efficiency and reliability in a professional property management context." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBjtIX0PiZN-BIF7SJLNAjxpUcY51wjUxeClvJL_SG_-igobu0IyZRHfDRlIzKPVKa8cRUUZfb0uW-o6JOCAWRWXaYDzlfaqvhxc0w2Gwb5lQdgZKxWSMonM_WLsq7kpRFr7gPSyDU3e_sbubwZt3fSjKXMNps-gna9LQCCwkrYWbeb4iPdCXul2IrIe5WAkAlg8vjEXAo2nHQs_0qF7JflH4QLHeqBLU_ce3OCbYQHEAIpVeQRK6g8vp_Pf9UHn0kAYVPNtR-gxyQH" />
                                <button class="absolute top-2 right-2 bg-surface/80 p-1.5 rounded-full shadow hover:bg-white transition-colors">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">close</span>
                                </button>
                            </div>
